    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Discretization error GCI of 2.4% and output comparison MAPE of 4.1% are within acceptance thresholds. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is satisfied for all 5 CPB operating points. The simulation is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; note that the ed25519 signature was declared but not finalised — downstream verifiers should flag the absence of a completed signature value.",
